data.description: Step into this contemporary 4-bed, 2-bath home designed with eco-conscious features. Equipped with solar panels and a battery backup system, alongside an EV charger and prewired ethernet for seamless connectivity, this home epitomizes modern sustainable living. Benefit from solar power, providing energy efficiency, cost savings, and the added security of a battery backup.  The thoughtfully designed property harmonizes style and sustainability, offering spacious bedrooms, open living areas, and an updated kitchen with modern amenities. Upgraded floors add elegance, while prewired ethernet ensures high-speed connectivity.    Outside, eco-friendly upgrades contribute to a greener lifestyle. Nestled in a tranquil neighborhood, this home embodies modern, sustainable living—a fusion of comfort, style, connectivity, and environmental awareness. It's a contemporary haven that not only embraces modernity but also stands as a beacon for a more sustainable future. Welcome to a home that champions contemporary living while paving the way for a greener tomorrow.
